---
title: 'About'
tagline: 'Creative Front End Developer, writer, music nerd.'
layout: default
bookCollections: CfctG
---

<div class="col-start-1 col-span-6 z-[1] mdw:fl-pt-3xl">
    <h1 class="h1 heading !text-[70px] mdw:!text-[80px] font-bold tracking-[-0.04em] !leading-[0.85]">{{ title | lower }}</h1>
    <span class="text-blue/[0.85] font-bold">{{ tagline | lower }}</span>
</div>
<div class="fl-pb-xl fl-my-xl col-start-1 col-span-full">
    <div class="mdw:max-w-[850px]">
        <div class="fl-text-step-1 font-bold tracking-[-0.04em]">{{ intro }}</div>
        <div class="fl-mt-s">{{ text | safe }}</div>
        <div class="fl-mt-l">
            <h3 class="heading fl-text-step-4">Now</h3>
            {% edge %}
            <div class="fl-mt-xs">
                Latest track from Last.FM: <span class="font-bold">{{ lastPlayedTrack }}</span> by <span class="font-bold">{{ lastPlayedArtist }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="fl-mt-xs">
                Over the past 7 days, I've also listened to
                {% for artist in tracks %}{% if loop.index != 1 %}{% if loop.last %} and {% elseif loop.index != 2 %}, {% endif %}<span class="font-bold">{{ artist.name }}</span>{% endif %}{% endfor %}
            </div>
            {% endedge %}
            <div class="fl-mt-xs">
              I'm also currently posting an album a day for a year that I enjoy, here's the <a class="underline hover:no-underline underline-offset-2" href="/365albums/">current list</a>.
            </div>
            <div class="fl-mt-xs">Current working as:
                {% set career = about.career[0] %}
                <span class="font-bold">{{ career.role }}</span>
                for
                <a href="{{ career.companyLink }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    <span class="font-bold">{{ career.company }}</span>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="fl-mt-xs">My latest post is:
                {% for post in collections.writing | reverse | limit(1) %}
                    <a
                        class="underline hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
                        href="{{ post.url }}"
                    >
                        <span class="font-bold">
                            {{ post.data.title }}
                        </span>
                    </a>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
            <div class="fl-mt-xs">Currently reading:
                <ul class="list-disc fl-pl-m fl-mt-s">
                {% set books = 'p9twg' | booksApi %}
                {% for item in books %}
                    <li>
                        <span class="font-bold">{{ item.title }}</span>
                        by
                        <span class="font-bold">{{ item.authors }}</span>
                    </li>
                {% endfor %}
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
